│  ├─ challenge #D6D9DE: needs training pipeline and release governance.
│  └─ mutate: start with inference ABI now, swap in learned model later without UI changes.
├─ loop_34 synthesize #FFC857
│  ├─ build: "Pack Budget Tiers": 64 MB, 160 MB, 320 MB, 700 MB.
│  ├─ challenge #D6D9DE: too many tiers confuse users.
